      "span_text": "Together, these experiments not only support the preferential localization of ␣-synuclein in presynaptic terminals adjacent to synapsin, but also suggest that this localization depends, at least in part, on the binding of ␣-synuclein to synaptobrevin-2  , whereas the localization of synaptobrevin-2 is independent of synucleins.",
